# Docusaurus Config

`docusaurus.config.js` controls site-wide behavior. Key settings in this project:

- `onBrokenLinks: 'throw'` — any bad link fails the build
- Mermaid enabled via `markdown.mermaid` and `@docusaurus/theme-mermaid`
- `markdown.format: 'detect'` — auto-detect MD vs MDX
- Theme: classic preset; custom CSS at `src/css/custom.css`

## When editing

- Keep changes scoped to what the user requested (navbar, footer, plugins, theme).
- After config changes, run `pnpm build` to verify.
- Update placeholder URLs (`url`, `organizationName`, `editUrl`) only when the user asks.
